snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Speed Freeks - Official Gameplay Trailer | Skulls 2024
snippet.description:
Take a look at this trailer for Warhammer 40k: Speed Freeks that was revealed at the Warhammer Skulls 2024 event.

In the 41st Millennium, a kult of speed-obsessed Orks have emerged  to gather an immense Speedwaaagh! 
These ‘Speed Freeks’ are addicted to high-speed combat with the fastest, shootiest, pulse-pounding, brain-rattling, combination of dakka andrecklessness, they bring their supercharged mob of buggies and tanks into the Speedwaaagh!  Hell-bent on gunning down their rivals and trashing everything in their path, these Orks race through battle attempting to prove themselves as “da fastest Orks in all da galaxy”.
